		{
			"id": "1e677c88-a0cf-4e91-b3bf-507cffa05b97",
			"name": "1e677c88-a0cf-4e91-b3bf-507cffa05b97",
			"type": "therapy",
			"content": {
				"number": "2",
				"title": "<a class=\"crossref\" id=\"15832\"></a>Behandling av brist på <a class=\"crossref\" id=\"vitamin B12-brist\"></a>vitamin B<sub>12</sub> och <a class=\"crossref\" id=\"folsyrabrist\"></a>folat",
				"id": "d1_45",
				"text": "<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\">\r\n<p><strong>Behandling av brist p&aring; B<sub>12</sub><a class=\"tableFootnoteLink\" href=\"#fnote_48\"><sup>a</sup></a></strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Remissionsbehandling</strong></div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Cyanokobalamin 2 mg peroralt 2 g&aring;nger dagligen i 1 m&aring;nad <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">eller</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Hydroxokobalamin 1 mg injiceras intramuskul&auml;rt eller subkutant var till</div>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">varannan dag i 7&ndash;14 dagar</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Underh&aring;llsbehandling</strong></div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Cyanokobalamin 1 mg peroralt dagligen <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">eller</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Hydroxokobalamin 1 mg injiceras med 1&ndash;3 m&aring;naders intervall (se produkt-</div>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">resum&eacute;/Fass)</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\">\r\n<p><strong>Behandling av brist p&aring; folat<a class=\"tableFootnoteLink\" href=\"#fnote_49\"><sup>b</sup></a></strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Remissionsbehandling</strong></div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Folsyra 1 mg, 2 tabletter 2&ndash;3 g&aring;nger/dag i ca 2 veckor</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Underh&aring;llsbehandling</strong></div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Folsyra 1 mg, 1 tablett 1 g&aring;ng dagligen</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\" class=\"footNotes\">\r\n<div class=\"tableFootnote\" id=\"fnote_48\">a. <span class=\"tabstop\"></span>Vid sv&aring;ra akuta fall med fastst&auml;lld eller misst&auml;nkt neuropati b&ouml;r initialt intensiv parenteral behandling ges intramuskul&auml;rt eller subkutant (se produktresum&eacute;/Fass).<span class=\"tabstop\"></span><span class=\"tab\"></span>Vid uttalad anemi b&ouml;r S-ferritin m&auml;tas f&ouml;r att best&auml;mma j&auml;rnf&ouml;rr&aring;dens storlek, eftersom j&auml;rnbrist kan uppst&aring; n&auml;r Hb-niv&aring;n korrigeras. J&auml;rnsubstitution tillr&aring;ds om S-ferritin &auml;r &lt;&nbsp;100 <span>&mu;</span>g/l vid terapistart.</div>\r\n<div class=\"tableFootnote\" id=\"fnote_49\">b. <span class=\"tabstop\"></span>B<sub>12</sub>-brist m&aring;ste uteslutas innan folsyrabehandling inleds eftersom en B<sub>12</sub>-brist kan maskeras och d&auml;rav beroende neurologiska symtom progrediera.</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>"
			},
